plot: A magazine article about promiscuity at the Inn leads Rhonda to crack down on Neal's antics.

When a gossip magazine prints an anonymous article about sex in the workplace concerning a supervisor at the Inn, Rhonda and the others jump to the conclusion that Neal is the unnamed employee. Rhonda arranges for sexual-harassment training for her staff, but soon discovers that practicing what she preaches isn't that easy.—Ron Kerrigan <mvg@whidbey.com>
